text: Kamishak Bay is a bay on the coast of Alaska in the United States. The proposed United States Navy seaplane tender USS Kamishak (AVP-44) was named for Kamishak Bay, but the contract for the ship's construction was cancelled in 1943 before construction began. ==References== * (ship namesake paragraph) Category:Bays of Alaska Category:Bodies of water of Kenai Peninsula Borough, Alaska
title: Kamishak Bay
